    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078978_3_397-485",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "397-485",
      "markText": "于无聊处有趣， 于无情节处有故事， 于无人问津处有激情。",
      "totalCount": 210,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300078978&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=397&rangeEnd=485",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/04c32480813ab8559g018b71?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=397&rangeEnd=485"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078978_7_7327-7370",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "7327-7370",
      "markText": "这时太宗驾着驴车一路南逃，才最终得以幸免，若非“车技”出神入化，太宗此役恐怕性命不保。",
      "totalCount": 192,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300078978&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=7327&rangeEnd=7370",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/04c32480813ab8559g018b71?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=7327&rangeEnd=7370"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078978_8_5420-5501",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "5420-5501",
      "markText": "英宗幼年时曾被收养在宫中一段时间，他的亲生父亲濮王赵允让一生共有二十七个儿子，一百二十六个孙子，五百一十三个曾孙，儿孙满堂，可谓当时赵宋皇室中最能“生”儿子的人。",
      "totalCount": 187,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300078978&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=5420&rangeEnd=5501",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/04c32480813ab8559g018b71?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=5420&rangeEnd=5501"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078978_6_7502-7533",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "7502-7533",
      "markText": "可他对待契丹求取仁宗画像的偏激心态，却真是焚琴煮鹤，大煞风景。",
      "totalCount": 170,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300078978&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=7502&rangeEnd=7533",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/04c32480813ab8559g018b71?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=7502&rangeEnd=7533"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078978_6_5682-5722",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "5682-5722",
      "markText": "因为此次契丹使臣耶律防是一位人物画的高手，他此行目的就是来“偷画”宋仁宗的御容。",
      "totalCount": 162,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300078978&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=5682&rangeEnd=5722",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/04c32480813ab8559g018b71?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=5682&rangeEnd=5722"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078978_7_2389-2411",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "2389-2411",
      "markText": "因为如果是画像的话，抱着的举动就有些怪异了。",
      "totalCount": 162,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300078978&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2389&rangeEnd=2411",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/04c32480813ab8559g018b71?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2389&rangeEnd=2411"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078978_6_19176-19264",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "19176-19264",
      "markText": "令人意想不到的是，宋徽宗的悲剧命运居然是因为“偷看”了辽天祚帝的画像，在看过辽天祚帝的“尊容”后，他踌躇满志地走上了背弃宋辽百年交情的不归路，联合新兴的金朝发动了收复燕云之役。",
      "totalCount": 156,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300078978&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=19176&rangeEnd=19264",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/04c32480813ab8559g018b71?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=19176&rangeEnd=19264"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078978_6_11532-11599",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "11532-11599",
      "markText": "这是宋人眼中真宗一生中最高光的时刻，当然，真宗自己的真实感受也许刚刚相反，事后回想起这次以万乘之尊被迫亲涉险地的窘境，他是不寒而栗的。",
      "totalCount": 154,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300078978&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=11532&rangeEnd=11599",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/04c32480813ab8559g018b71?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=11532&rangeEnd=11599"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078978_7_11348-11428",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "11348-11428",
      "markText": "徐铉把和平稳定、经济发展当作了太平的成就加以宣扬，不再打仗，就是太平；老百姓有饭吃，就是太平。给太宗朝的太平，定了全新的基调。太宗对这样的太平之道，也是心领神会",
      "totalCount": 153,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300078978&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=11348&rangeEnd=11428",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/04c32480813ab8559g018b71?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=11348&rangeEnd=11428"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078978_7_14554-14569",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "14554-14569",
      "markText": "远胜乾隆的那些狗屁不通的诗句。",
      "totalCount": 150,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300078978&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=14554&rangeEnd=14569",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/04c32480813ab8559g018b71?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=14554&rangeEnd=14569"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078978_9_7940-7985",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "7940-7985",
      "markText": "其实，东南的王者气，大概预示的是宋室南渡的历史以及宋代皇帝御容像的最终归宿是在江南的结局。",
      "totalCount": 150,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300078978&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=7940&rangeEnd=7985",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/04c32480813ab8559g018b71?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=7940&rangeEnd=7985"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078978_13_1201-1278",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "1201-1278",
      "markText": "高宗活了八十一岁，是宋代最长寿的皇帝。除了那个在晚年自己瞎折腾、最后把自己搞得活活饿死的梁武帝以外，高宗可以说是秦、汉以来一百三十多个皇帝中享寿最长久者。",
      "totalCount": 135,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300078978&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=1201&rangeEnd=1278",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/04c32480813ab8559g018b71?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=1201&rangeEnd=1278"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078978_13_18721-18820",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "18721-18820",
      "markText": "神宗把每年收上来的金银财宝分库收藏，每一个库房就用这首五言绝句的一个字命名，就可以齐集二十库的财宝，那就可以为开疆拓土累积到足够的军费了，他用这样的方式来激励自己好好存钱，可谓在“诗坛”别开生面了。",
